elements.name: As an admin user I can create an untitled post, by clicking on the title

steps.name: I enter "<ADMIN_USER>" into input field having id "ember8"
I enter "<ADMIN_PASSWORD>" into input field having id "ember10"
I click on element having css selector "button.login"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-btn.gh-btn-green.ember-view"
I click on element having css selector "textarea.gh-editor-title.ember-text-area.gh-input.ember-view"
I click on element having css selector "a.blue.link.fw4.flex.items-center.ember-view"
I should see text "(Untitled)" in posts section
I check that post with title "(Untitled)" is not published
